                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.974
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Targets for these experiments",
                "were prepared by electrodeposition of lead to a",
                "thickness of 1 mg/cm2 onto thin nickel foil. The",
                "target material consisted of highly enriched",
                "206Pb (97.4%). The recoil catchers were prepared of",
                "very pure (99.999%) aluminum foil having a surface",
                "density of 5 mg/cm2. Stacks consisting of six",
                "target-catcher pairs were mounted in a target holder",
                "which also served as a Faraday cup for determination",
                "of the beam intensity."
              ]
            }
